en_9881087_0	COLOMBO (News 1st) – A drug dealer who was was selling Heroin via “eZ cash” was arrested in Horana.
en_9881087_1	The police stated that the suspect had rented three houses in Horana and Welikala in order to run the drug racket.
en_9881087_2	Police found 25 grams of Heroin in his possession.
en_9881087_3	The 33-year-old suspect, a resident of Rathnapura was arrested while he was traveling in a car.
en_9881087_4	It was revealed that the police had filed cases against him in connection to jewelry heists and drug trafficking in the past.
